	   <tr><td colspan=2>I have read and/ or heard both sides of the story, but what is true? Who is better: A Monk or a Warrior? I read that Monks aren't as good in the earlier levels, but once they get really high up there, a Warrior won't be able to lay a finger on them. Is that true? I realize that Monk's have a major AC loss for armor, and their weapon selection is limited. If that is so, how can they manage to still be the ultimate melee class? Thank you.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
